lRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Putting It Together: Machine Translation Example"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"yaml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Step 1: ENCODER reads English phrase\n  Input: [\"I\", \"love\", \"AI\"]\n  ↓\n  Processes \"I\" → updates state\n  Processes \"love\" → updates state\n  Processes \"AI\" → updates state\n  ↓\n  Output: Context Vector (compressed meaning)\n\nStep 2: DECODER unpacks meaning\n  Input: Context Vector\n  ↓\n  Generates \"Ja\" → uses \"Ja\" for next\n  Generates \"aime\" → uses \"aime\" for next\n  Generates \"AI\" → uses \"AI\" for next\n  ↓\n  Output: [\"Ja\", \"aime\", \"AI\"] (French)\n\nResult: \"I love AI\" → \"Ja aime AI\""}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"How It Works: Text Summarization Example"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"yaml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Step 1: ENCODER reads long article\n  Input: [Full article with hundreds of words]\n  ↓\n  Processes word by word, capturing key points\n  ↓\n  Output: Context Vector (compressed summary)\n\nStep 2: DECODER generates short summary\n  Input: Context Vector\n  ↓\n  Generates: \"The\" → \"study\" → \"shows\" → \"benefits\" → \".\"\n  ↓\n  Output: [\"The\", \"study\", \"shows\", \"benefits\", \".\"]\n\nResult: Long article → Short concise summary capturing key points"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The model captures key points without just copying sentences."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Key Challenges with Basic Encoder-Decoder"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Challenge"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":